s%20of%20insufficient%20consumption%20of%2015%20micronutrients%20across%20185%20countries%2C%20taken%20through%20diets%20without%20the%20use%20of%20supplements%2C%20according%20to%20an%20international%20team%2C%20including%20researchers%20from%20Harvard%20University%2C%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20suggested%20that%20around%20the%20world%2C%20almost%2070%20per%20cent%2C%20or%20over%20five%20billion%2C%20people%20do%20not%20consume%20enough%20iodine%2C%20vitamin%20E%2C%20and%20calcium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20also%20found%20that%20within%20a%20country%20and%20an%20age%20group%2C%20more%20women%20were%20consuming%20inadequate%20amounts%20of%20iodine%2C%20vitamin%20B12%20and%20iron%2C%20compared%20to%20men%2C%20whereas%20more%20men%20were%20consuming%20inadequate%20amounts%20of%20magnesium%2C%20vitamin%20B6%2C%20zinc%20and%20vitamin%20C%2C%20compared%20to%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20while%20more%20women%20consumed%20insufficient%20amounts%20of%20iodine%2C%20compared%20to%20men%2C%20more%20men%20consumed%20inadequate%20amounts%20of%20zinc%20and%20magnesium%2C%20compared%20to%20women%2C%20the%20team%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20analyses%20over%20the%20past%2010%20years%20have%20looked%20at%20micronutrient%20deficiencies%2C%20the%20researchers%20said%20large%20data%20gaps%20remain%20for%20many%20micronutrients%20and%20population%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20study%2C%20the%20authors%20used%20publicly%20available%20data%20from%20the%20Global%20Dietary%20Database%20to%20estimate%20the%20prevalence%20of%20insufficient%20nutrient%20intakes%20for%2099.3%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20global%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMen%20and%20women%20aged%2010-30%20years%20were%20most%20prone%20to%20low-levels%20of%20calcium%20intake%2C%20especially%20in%20South%20Asia%2C%20Southeast%20Asia%20and%20sub-Saharan%20Africa%2C%20the%20team%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20said%20that%20the%20findings%20could%20be%20used%20by%20public%20health%20professionals%20to%20target%20populations%20in%20need%20of%20dietary%20interventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20since%20they%20did%20not%20account%20for%20intake%20of%20fortified%20foods%20or%20supplements%2C%20the%20results%20could%20possibly%20be%20an%20overestimate%20for%20some%20key%20nutrients%20in%20particular%20locations%20where%20people%20consume%20high%20amounts%20of%20fortified%20foods%20and%20supplements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724980800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ftib0u67o_medicine-generic_625x300_25_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flancet-study-says-indians-deficient-in-iron-calcium-folate-6448875%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22People%20across%20all%20age%20groups%20in%20India%2C%20both%20men%20and%20women%2C%20are%20consuming%20inadequate%20amounts%20of%20micronutrients%20critical%20for%20health%2C%20including%20iron%2C%20calcium%20and%20folate%2C%20as%20estimated%20in%20a%20study%20published%20in%20The%20Lancet%20Global%20Health%20journal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Stree%202'%20box%20office%20collection%20day%2015%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724980406000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112909991%2Cimgsize-25548.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fstree-2-box-office-collection-day-15-the-shraddha-kapoor-rajkummar-rao-is-now-the-sixth-highest-grossing-hindi-movie-of-all-times-getting-past-kgf-2%2Farticleshow%2F112910001.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%2