rd%20for%20the%20actors%20association%20%C2%A0which%20means%20she%20cannot%20even%20work%20for%20television%20serials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20add%20insult%20to%20injury%2C%20no%20headway%20is%20made%20in%20investigations%20into%20sexual%20harassment%20allegations%20in%20Tamil%20cinema%2C%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20read%20that%20Suresh%20Gopi%20has%20said%20'Where%20is%20the%20proof'.%20How%20can%20anyone%20give%20proof%3F%20They%20can%20do%20lie-detector%20test%20like%20the%20CBI%20is%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnState%20minister%20Swaminathan%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20authorities%20have%20not%20received%20any%20complaints%20about%20sexual%20harassment%20from%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKutti%20Padmini%20said%20even%20she%20was%20sexually%20harassed%20as%20a%20child%20artist.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20thrown%20out%20of%20a%20Hindi%20film%20when%20my%20mom%20raised%20the%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20explaining%20the%20difficulties%20in%20building%20evidence%20against%20perpetrators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%20is%20facing%20a%20major%20crisis%20after%20the%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee%20report%20on%20harassment%20faced%20by%20women%20in%20the%20industry%20was%20made%20public%20earlier%20this%20month.%20It%20contains%20accounts%20alleging%20harassment%2C%20exploitation%2C%20and%20ill-treatment%20of%20women%20professionals.%20It%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20spate%20of%20allegations%20from%20various%20women%20artistes%20and%20other%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20formed%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20to%20investigate%20the%20matter.%20%26quot%3BThe%20SIT%20has%20been%20strengthened%20by%20including%20additional%20women%20officers.%20All%20related%20cases%20registered%20at%20local%20police%20stations%20are%20to%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20SIT%20for%20further%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Kerala%20Police%20have%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724979360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fiimguu4g_kutti-padmini-ndtv_625x300_30_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%2Factor-kutti-padmini-says-sexual-harassment-rampant-in-tamil-film-industry-6449261%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ripples%20of%20the%20massive%20shake%20up%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%20over%20massive%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20exploitation%2C%20has%20reached%20neighbouring%20Tamil%20Nadu.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nifty%20FMCG%20shows%20signs%20of%20near%20term%20correction%3B%20check%20key%20levels%20here%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724979153000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-07%2F07%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1720368385-832.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fnifty-fmcg-shows-signs-of-near-term-correction-check-key-levels-here-124083000061_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Support%20levels%20are%20crucial%20in%20this%20corrective%20phase%2C%20and%20for%20the%20Nifty%20FMCG%20Index%2C%20key%20support%20levels%20are%20identified%20at%2061%2C180%20and%2059%2C500.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fnifty-fmcg-shows-signs-of-near-term-correction-check-key-levels-here-124083000061_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fnifty-fmcg-shows-signs-of-near-term-correction-check-key-levels-here-124083000061_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fnifty-fmcg-shows-signs-of-near-term-correction-check-