ow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Flavender-ai-israeli-army-gaza%2F%5C%22%3E%2B972%20Magazine%20and%20Local%20Call%3C%2Fa%3E%20reveals%20some%20disturbing%20details%20from%20Israel's%20bombing%20campaign%2C%20especially%20how%20the%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20fully%20relied%20on%20a%20tool%20for%20its%20bombing%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Lavender'%20and%20its%20use%20case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELavender%2C%20developed%20by%20Israel's%20elite%20intelligence%20division%2C%20Unit%208200%2C%20operates%20as%20an%20AI-powered%20database%20designed%20to%20identify%20potential%20targets%20linked%20to%20Hamas%20and%20Palestinian%20Islamic%20Jihad%20(PIJ).%20Lavender%20uses%20machine%20learning%20algorithms%20and%20processes%20vast%20amounts%20of%20data%20to%20pinpoint%20individuals%20deemed%20%26quot%3Bjunior%26quot%3B%20militants%20within%20these%20armed%20groups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELavender%20initially%20identified%20as%20many%20as%2037%2C000%20Palestinian%20men%20associated%20with%20Hamas%20or%20PIJ.%20The%20usage%20of%20AI%20to%20identify%20targets%20marks%20a%20significant%20change%20in%20how%20the%20Israeli%20intelligence%20apparatus%2C%20Mossad%20and%20Shin%20Bet%2C%20function%20-%20relying%20on%20more%20labour-intensive%20human%20decision-making.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fo4og57oo_deir-elbalah-gaza-israel-strike_625x300_27_August_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoldiers%20often%20made%20decisions%20in%20as%20little%20as%2020%20seconds%20to%20determine%20whether%20to%20bomb%20these%20identified%20targets%20based%20on%20Lavender's%20information%2C%20primarily%20to%20ascertain%20the%20gender%20of%20the%20target.%20Human%20soldiers%20frequently%20followed%20the%20machine's%20information%20unquestioningly%2C%20despite%20the%20AI%20program's%20error%20margin%20of%20up%20to%2010%20per%20cent%2C%20meaning%20it%20could%20be%20incorrect%20up%20to%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20program%20often%20targeted%20individuals%20with%20minimal%20or%20no%20affiliation%20with%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGospel%20-%20Israel's%20Another%20AI%20Arm%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESystems%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BGospel%26quot%3B%20are%20being%20used%20to%20allow%20automatic%20tools%20to%20produce%20targets%20at%20a%20fast%20pace%2C%20and%20works%20by%20improving%20accurate%20and%20high-quality%20intelligence%20material%20according%20to%20the%20requirement%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20IDF%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWith%20the%20help%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20and%20through%20the%20rapid%20and%20automatic%20extraction%20of%20updated%20intelligence%20-%20it%20produces%20a%20recommendation%20for%20the%20researcher%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20being%20that%20there%20will%20be%20a%20complete%20match%20between%20the%20machine's%20recommendation%20and%20the%20identification%20performed%20by%20a%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20IDF%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20platforms%20crunch%20data%20to%20select%20targets%20for%20air%20strikes.%20Ensuing%20raids%20can%20then%20be%20rapidly%20assembled%20with%20another%20artificial%20intelligence%20model%20called%20Fire%20Factory%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22no%20index%2C%20no%20follow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-07-16%2Fisrael-using-ai-systems-to-plan-deadly-military-operations%5C%22%3E%20Bloomberg%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Fire%20Factory%20calculates%20munition%20loads%2C%20prioritizes%20and%20assigns%20thousands%20of%20targets%20to%20aircraft%20and%20drones%2C%20and%20proposes%20a%20schedule%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20by%20%2B972%20Magazine%20mentions%20the%20book%20'The%20Human-Machine%20Team%3A%20How%20to%20Create%20Synergy%20Between%20Human%20and%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20That%20Will%20Revolutionize%20Our%20World'.%20The%20author%20'Brigadier%20General%20YS'%2C%20who%20is%20reportedly%20the%20commander%20of%20the%208200%20Intelligence%20Unit%20of%20Israel%2C%20makes%20a%20case%20for%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20defence%26quot%3B%20and%20gives%20scenarios%20that%20could%20threaten%20Israel%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20chapter%20%26quot%3BDeep%20Defense%3A%26quot%3B%20New%20Potentials%2C%20the%20author%20says%20%26quot%3BDeep%20defence%20is%20the%20ability%20of%20national%20establishments%20to%20use%20The%20Human-Machine%20Team%20concept%20to%20address%20security%20challenges%20to%20expose%20issues%20in%20new%20ways%20that%20were%20heretofore%20impossible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Human-Machine%20Team%20should%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20identify%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20targets%20before%20the%20battle%20begins%20and%20thousands%20of%20targets%20should%20be%20identified%20every%20day.%20The%20author%20makes%20a%20case%20where%20he%20explains%20why%20it%20is%20important%20to%20create%20such%20tools%20so%20that%20the%20military%20can%20strike%20at%20the%20right%20targets%20at%20the%20right%20time%20with%20less%20collateral%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20About%20AI%20in%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20War%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20begets%20AI.%20The%20use%20of%20automated%20tools%20like%20unmanned%20FPV%20drones%2C%20and%20robots%20has%20reduced%20the%20human-risk%20factor%20for%20warring%20nations%20but%20has%20increased%20the%20dependency%20on%20technology%2C%20which%20seems%20like%20a%20win-win%20situation%20for%20a%20nation%20but%20the%20ethical%20and%20legal%20concerns%20of%20using%20AI%20are%20always%20followed%20by%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20is%20a%20testing%20lab%20for%20future%20tools%20for%20fighting%20in%20combat.%20The%20concept%20of%20drone%20attacks%20has%20proliferated%20to%20different%20conflicts%20in%20different%20regions%2C%20especially%20non-state%20actors%20like%20Houthi%20rebels%20and%20Hezbollah%20fighting%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deployment%20of%20automated%20drones%20does%20not%20simply%20define%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20conflict.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F3un9tu5g_ukraine-drone_625x300_10_January_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20primarily%20used%20to%20analyze%20geospatial%20intelligence%20by%20processing%20satellite%20images%20and%20decoding%20open-source%20intelligence%20like%20videos%2C%20and%20photos%20available%20online.%20Surveillance%20drone%20footage%2C%20on-ground%20human%20intelligence%20(HUMINT)%2C%20satellite%20images%2C%20and%20open-source%20data%20are%20all%20combined%20and%20processed%20by%20AI%20tools%20to%20deliver%20an%20outcome%20that%20is%20used%20to%20conduct%20missions.%20This%20represents%20the%20use%20of%20data%20analytics%20on%20the%20battlefield.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20National%20Defense%20magazine%2C%20Ukraine%20reportedly%20used%20Clearview%20AI%2C%20a%20software%20tool%20from%20a%20US-based%20firm%2C%20for%20facial%20recognition%20to%20identify%20dead%20soldiers%20and%20Russian%20assailants%20and%20combat%20misinformation.%20US%20firms%20like%20Primer%20have%20deployed%20tools%20to%20decode%20Russian%20encrypted%20messages%20delivered%20through%20radio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ukraine%20is%20working%20on%20developing%20AI-enabled%20drones%20to%20counter%20radio%20jamming.%20Cheap%20FPV%20drones%2C%20widely%20used%20for%20several%20months%2C%20have%20witnessed%20a%20drop%20in%20their%20hits%20due%20to%20the%20jamming%20of%20radio%20signals%2C%20a%20form%20of%20Electronic%20Warfare%20which%20Russians%20are%20masters%20of.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20already%20working%20with%20the%20concept%20that%20soon%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20connection%20on%20the%20front%20line%26quot%3B%20between%20pilot%20and%20UAV%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22no%20index%2C%20no%20follow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Fukraine-rushes-create-ai-enabled-war-drones-2024-07-18%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAI%2520is%2520already%2520being%2520used%2Chundreds%2520of%2520kilometres%2520inside%2520Russia.%5C%22%3EReuters%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20quoting%20Max%20Makarchuk%2C%20the%20AI%20lead%20for%20Brave1%2C%20a%20defence%20tech%20accelerator%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Ukrainian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadio%20jamming%20blocks%20the%20operator's%20contact%20with%20the%20munition%20(a%20drone)%20by%20forming%20a%20protective%20invisible%20layer%20around%20the%20target%2C%20therefore%20resulting%20in%20damage%20to%20the%20drone.%20Automating%20the%20final%20part%20of%20the%20drone's%20flight%20can%20enable%20success.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22no%20follow%2C%20no%20index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frusi.org%2Fexplore-our-research%2Fpublications%2Fcommentary%2Fstruggling-not-crumbling-russian-defence-ai-time-war%5C%22%3ERussia%20is%20focusing%20on%20developing%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20systems%20to%20counter%20the%20West%20and%20fight%20Ukraine%20on%20the%20battlefield.%20If%20numbers%20are%20compared%20then%20Russia%20is%20way%20ahead%20of%20Ukraine%20in%20terms%20of%20military%20prowess%20but%20the%20Red%20Army%20has%20suffered%20huge%20losses%20on%20the%20battlefield.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAreas%20like%20increasing%20command%2C%20control%20and%20communication%20with%20AI-enabled%20decision-making%2C%20developing%20smarter%20weapons%2C%20which%20it%20calls%20%26quot%3Bintellectualization%20of%20weapons%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20developing%20more%20unmanned%20aerial%2Fground%20vehicles%20and%20AI-enabled%20guidance%20systems%20for%20missiles%2C%20are%20in%20Moscow's%20focus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20maker%20of%20the%20Russian%20Kamikaze%20drone%20KUB-LA%2C%20ZALA%20Aero%20Group%2C%20claims%20it%20is%20capable%20of%20selecting%20and%20engaging%20targets%20using%20AI.%20The%20Lancet-3%20loitering%20munition%20is%20highly%20autonomous%20and%20the%20use%20of%20sensors%20enables%20it%20to%20locate%20and%20destroy%20a%20target%20without%20human%20guidance%2C%20even%20being%20capable%20of%20returning%20to%20the%20operator%20if%20a%20target%20has%20not%20been%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20a%20Russian%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22no%20index%2C%20no%20follow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fria.ru%2F20230524%2Fspetsoperatsiya-1873760329.html%5C%22%3ES-350%20Vityaz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20surface-to-air-missile%20reportedly%20shot%20down%20an%20aircraft%20in%20autonomous%20mode%2C%20which%20was%20claimed%20as%20the%20first%20AI-enable%20missile%20kill.%20The%20system%20detected%2C%20tracked%20and%20destroyed%20a%20Ukrainian%20air%20target%20without%20human%20assistance.%20The%20claim%20remains%20contested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeavy%20investment%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20border%20reaffirms%20the%20central%20role%20of%20AI%20in%20war%20and%20how%20future%20wars%20could%20be%20co-commanded%20by%20technology%20and%20a%20human.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724968380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fmq9rsdc_gaza-august-2024-afp-_625x300_10_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-war-explained-how-ai-is-leading-israels-bombing-campaign-in-gaza-6448734%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel's%20military%20campaign%20in%20Gaza%20-%20which%20started%20after%20the%20deadly%20October%207%20last%20year%20in%20which%20over%201%2C100%20people%20were%20brutally%20killed%