ng%20Man.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBurning%20Man%20is%20devoted%20to%20acts%20of%20gift%20giving%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20reads%20in%20Burning%20Man's%20official%2010%20guiding%20principles.%20%26quot%3BThe%20value%20of%20a%20gift%20is%20unconditional.%20Gifting%20does%20not%20contemplate%20a%20return%20or%20an%20exchange%20for%20something%20of%20equal%20value.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20find%20all%20kinds%20of%20gifts%20among%20the%20thousands%20of%20camps%20that%20fill%20the%20playa.%20And%20unlike%20the%20gifts%20you%20usually%20get%20for%20your%20birthday%20or%20the%20holidays%2C%20they%20won't%20be%20store-bought%20(decommodification%20is%20another%20of%20the%2010%20principles).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20camps%20that%20offer%20manicures%20and%20foot%20massages%20and%20camps%20that%20offer%20New%20York-style%20breakfast%20sandwiches.%20You'll%20find%20open%20bars%20on%20every%20corner%2C%20often%20accompanied%20by%20creative%20themes%20like%20being%20consensually%20abducted%20by%20%26quot%3Baliens%26quot%3B%20who%20capture%20you%20with%20a%20hula%20hoop%20and%20then%20shower%20you%20with%20compliments%20(this%20is%20a%20real%20camp%2C%20and%20it%20is%20awesome).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20camps%20throw%20parties%2C%20while%20others%20let%20you%20send%20postcards%20to%20your%20parents%20or%20dogs.%20My%20camp%2C%20Android%20Oasis%2C%20contributes%20a%20covered%20dome%20where%20anyone%20can%20stop%20by%20to%20cool%20down%20with%20ice-cold%20drinks%2C%20massages%2C%20and%20great%20music.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurning%20Man%20is%20also%20founded%20on%20radical%20self-reliance%2C%20so%20you%20shouldn't%20just%20show%20up%20with%20nothing%20but%20hope%20in%20the%20generosity%20of%20others%20(although%20some%20people%20do).%20Most%20Burners%20don't%20come%20to%20Black%20Rock%20City%20wondering%20what%20they%20can%20get%20from%20people%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20rather%20wha