0press%20release%20highlights%20new%20features%20for%20NFL%20season%2C%20but%20I'm%20still%20questioning%20why%20the%20app%20exists.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDid%20you%20know%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fapple-sports%2Fid6446788829%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esports%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20not%2C%20don't%20feel%20bad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20watch%20sports%2C%20and%20I%20know%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20spend%20time%20thinking%20about%20Apple%20and%20Apple%20products%2C%20and%20almost%20none%20of%20them%20ever%20mention%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-sports-app-is-here-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20Sports%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20launched%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20among%20the%20few%20people%20I%20know%20who%20%3Cem%3Edo%3C%2Fem%3E%20talk%20about%20the%20Apple%20Sports%20app%2C%20the%20conversation%20goes%20something%20like%20this%3A%20%26quot%3BWTF%20is%20with%20this%20app%3F%20Why%20does%20it%20exist%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20the%20Apple%20Sports%20app%20is%20the%20most%20bare-bones%20app%20you've%20ever%20seen.%20It%20has%20some%20%E2%80%94%20not%20all%2C%20not%20by%20a%20long%20shot%20%E2%80%94%20sports%20scores%2C%20and%20some%20sports%20betting%20odds%2C%20and%E2%80%A6%20that's%20it.%20That's%20the%20whole%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20some%20of%20us%20are%20talking%20about%20it%20today%2C%20again%2C%20is%20that%20Apple%20has%20put%20out%20a%20press%20release%20reminding%20us%20that%20the%20Apple%20Sports%20app%20exists%2C%20and%20that%20you'll%20be%20able%20to%20use%20it%20to%20find%20the%20scores%20of%20college%20football%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnfl-tv-ratings-playoffs-super