had%20a%20rare%20case%20of%20trichophagia%20--%20the%20compulsive%20habit%20of%20eating%20hair%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20Rapunzel%20syndrome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20parents%20were%20baffled%20by%20her%20repeated%20bouts%20of%20poor%20appetite%20and%20frequent%20vomiting%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years.%20They%20took%20her%20to%20many%20doctors%20including%20paediatricians%2C%20general%20physicians%2C%20and%20ENT%20specialists%20hoping%20to%20identify%20the%20problem%20and%20a%20cure%20for%20her%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20diagnosed%20Aditi's%20condition%20to%20be%20gastritis%20and%20prescribed%20pills%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20doctors%20at%20Aster's%20Children%20and%20Women%20Hospital%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20found%20that%20she%20had%20a%20trichobezoar%20--%20a%20term%20that%20describes%20all%20the%20hair%20mass%20that%20had%20accumulated%20in%20her%20gastrointestinal%20tract.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrichobezoar%20is%20an%20extremely%20rare%20condition%20and%20especially%20very%20rare%20in%20a%20child%20as%20young%20as%20Aditi.%20It%20is%20often%20associated%20with%20trichophagia%2C%20a%20psychological%20disorder%20where%20individuals%20eat%20hair.%20While%20commonly%20seen%20in%20adolescent%20girls%2C%20finding%20this%20in%20a%20much%20younger%20child%20highlights%20the%20uniqueness%20of%20this%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Manjiri%20Somashekhar%2C%20Lead%20and%20Senior%20Consultant%20-%20Paediatric%20Surgery%20told%20IANS%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20open%20stomach%20surgery%2C%20also%20known%20as%20laparotomy%2C%20had%20to%20be%20performed%20on%20Aditi%20because%20the%20hairball%20was%20very%20large%20and%20sticky%20and%20the%20situation%20was%20too%20complicated%20for%20an%20endoscopy%20to%20be%20performed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20method%2C%20which%20was%20done%20in%20a%20total%20of%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%2C%20proved%20fruitful%20because%20it%20prevented%20any%20leakage%20into%20the%20peritoneal%20cavity%2C%20the%20doctor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20left%20undiagnosed%2C%20her%20condition%20could%20have%20led%20to%20severe%20malnutrition%2C%20anaemia%2C%20and%20significant%20bleeding%20from%20the%20stomach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20surgery%2C%20she%20was%20placed%20on%20a%20special%20diet%20and%20continues%20to%20receive%20counselling%20and%20regular%20monitoring%2C%20the%20doctor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724953200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2Fi0lrb1n_doctor-generic_625x300_28_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdoctors-remove-cricket-ball-sized-hairball-from-8-year-olds-stomach-in-bengaluru-6447802%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20rare%20case%2C%20doctors%20in%20Bengaluru%20removed%20a%20massive%20hairball%20--%20as%20large%20as%20a%20cricket%20ball%20--%20from%20the%20stomach%20of%20an%208-year-old%20girl%2C%20the%20hospital%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Cop%20Seen%20Dancing%20At%20Colleague's%20Farewell%2C%20Dies%20Moments%20Later%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20young%20police%20officer%2C%20who%20was%20dancing%20at%20a%20farewell%20party%20in%20Delhi%2C%20died%20after%20probably%20suffering%20a%20heart%20attack.%20Ravi%20Kumar%2C%20the%20head%20constable%20in%20Delhi%20police%2C%20was%20enjoying%20the%20farewell%20party%20of%20a%20colleague%20when%20he%20suddenly%20experienced%20pain%20in%20his%20chest%20and%20collapsed.%20The%20incident%20happened%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20was%20immediately%20rushed%20to%20a%20nearby%20hospital%20but%20the%20doctors%20declared%20him%20dead.%20He%20was%2