%20approval%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20establish%20a%20comprehensive%20campus%20in%20the%20country.%20This%20move%20marks%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20the%20Indian%20education%20sector%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission's%20(UGC)%20initiative%20to%20invite%20the%20top%20500%20foreign%20universities%20to%20set%20up%20campuses%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20letter%20of%20intent%20(LoI)%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Southampton%20today%2C%20marking%20the%20formal%20beginning%20of%20this%20collaboration.%20The%20event%20took%20place%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%2C%20who%20emphasised%20the%20significance%20of%20this%20development%20under%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20reflects%20both%20the%20vision%20of%20elevating%20our%20educational%20standards%20to%20the%20highest%20global%20levels%20and%20delivering%20on%20the%20education%20pillar%20of%20India-UK%20cooperation%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Jaishankar%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20such%20endeavours%20will%20further%20prepare%20Indian%20youth%20for%20global%20challenges%20and%20foster%20international%20cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20Southampton%2C%20recognised%20as%20one%20of%20the%20top%20100%20universities%20globally%2C%20will%20establish%20its%20campus%20in%20the%20Delhi%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR).%20This%20campus%20will%20focus%20on%20education%2C%20research%2C%20knowledge%20exchange%2C%20and%20enterprise%20activities%2C%20integrating%20Southampton's%20world-class%20expertise%20with%20India's%20emerging%20potential%20as%20a%20global%20education%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMark%20E%20Smith%2C%20president%20and%20vice-chancellor%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Southampton%2C%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20this%20initiative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20no%20university%20can%20be%20truly%20global%20without%20engaging%20with%20India.%20We%20intend%20to%20establish%20a%20campus%20that%20delivers%20social%20value%20and%20economic%20impact%20to%20India%20and%20the%20university%20by%20bringing%20together%20Southampton's%20world-class%20activities%20in%20education%2C%20research%2C%20and%20knowledge%20exchange%20and%20enterprise%2C%20with%20all%20the%20talent%20of%20the%20rising%20global%20superpower%20that%20is%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20added%20that%20the%20new%20campus%20would%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20supporting%20the%20Government%20of%20India's%20transformative%20agenda%20by%20harnessing%20the%20potential%20of%20Indian%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Andrew%20Atherton%2C%20vice-president%20of%20International%20and%20Engagement%2C%20emphasised%20the%20campus's%20role%20in%20fostering%20academic%20collaboration%20and%20enhancing%20the%20Indian%20higher%20education%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUniversity%20of%20Southampton%20Delhi%20NCR%20will%20be%20the%20first%20comprehensive%20international%20campus%20in%20India.%20It%20will%20foster%20academic%20collaboration%20and%20bring%20an%20international%20dimension%20to%20the%20Indian%20higher%20education%20system%2C%20opening%20up%20opportunities%20to%20study%20for%20a%20top%20100%20degree%20in-country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20development%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20realizing%20the%20NEP%202020's%20vision%20of%20'internationalisation%20at%20home.'%20The%20Education%20Minister%20also%20lauded%20the%20growing%20interest%20of%20globally%20renowned%20higher%20education%20institutions%20(HEIs)%20in%20collaborating%20with%20Indian%20institutions%20and%20contributing%20to%20India's%20future%20as%20a%20global%20education%20and%20talent%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20only%20Australian%20universities-%20Deakin%20University%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Wollongong%20-%20have%20set%20up%20their%20campuses%20in%20India%2C%20at%20Gujarat%20International%20Finance%20Tec-City%20(GIFT%20City).%20Moreover%2C%20Malaysia's%20Lincoln%20University%20College%20was%20the%20first%20foreign%20university%20to%20register%20through%20the%20UGC's%20dedicated%20portal%20to%20set%20up%20a%20campus%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724949780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fobmu8h7_university-of-southampton_625x300_29_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Funiversity-of-southampton-becomes-first-uk-university-to-set-up-campus-in-india-6446694%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20letter%20of%20intent%20(LoI)%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Southampton%20today%2C%20marking%20the%20formal%20beginning%20of%20this%20collaboration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mumbai%20Property%20Dealer%20Gives%20Contract%20To%20Kill%20Friend.%20Then%2C%20A%20Plot%20Twist%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EContract%20Killing%20and%20then%20a%20miscalculation%20leading%20to%20a%20second%20death%20-%20these%20were%20what%20tied%20an%20abandoned%20car%20found%20near%20Mumbai%20and%20two%20missing%20property%20dealers%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20Police%20have%20found.%20The%20men%20in%20question%20-%20property%20dealers%20Aamir%20Khanzada%20and%20Sumit%20Jain%20-%20have%20been%20missing%20since%20August%2021.%20But%20the%20police%20had%20no%20clue%20till%20the%20Baleno%20car%20was%20found%20near%20Mumbai%20Pune%20Expressway%20two%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepak%20Sakore%2C%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20of%20Navi%20Mumbai%2C%20said%20the%20they%20found%20bullet%20marks%2C%20two%20empty%20cartridges%20and%20blood%20inside%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20breakthrough%20came%20when%20they%20arrested%20Vitthal%20Nakade%2C%20who%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20contract%20killer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sakore%20said%20Vitthal%20Nakade%20was%20a%20friend%20of%20Sumit.%20Amir%20Khanzada%20and%20Sumit%20Jain%2C%20the%20police%20found%2C%20were%20friends%20and%20business%20partners%20who%20had%20fallen%20out%20over%20a%20land%20deal.%20Both%20were%20residents%20of%20Nerul%20and%20were%20missing%20since%20the%20night%20of%20August%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecently%2C%20Sumit%20Jain%2C%20who%20%C2%A0had%20incurred%20massive%20debts%2C%20usurped%20a%20plot%20of%20land%20through%20fraud.%20Aamir%20was%20blackmailing%20him%20to%20get%20a%20share.%20So%20Sumit%20hired%20a%20contract%20killer%20to%20kill%20Aamir%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0It%20appeared%20that%20the%20entire%20planning%20was%20done%20by%20Sumit%20Jain%20and%20Vitthal%20Nakade%20in%20a%20day%20or%20two.%20The%20contract%20killer%20was%20given%20Rs.%2050%20lakh%2C%20the%20police%20were%20told%20by%20Nakade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20came%20the%20big%20twist.%20Instead%20of%20the%20body%20of%20Aamir%20Khanzada%2C%20the%20police%20found%20the%20body%20of%20Sumit%20Jain.%20The%20big%20question%20then%20became%20who%20killed%20Sumit%20and%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20Aamir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20big%20revelation%20came%20when%20the%20police%20arrested%20a%20few%20more%20men%20connected%20to%20Vitthal%20Nakade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20night%20of%20August%2021%2C%20at%2011%20pm%2C%20Sumit%20Jain%20and%20Vitthal%20Nakhade%20had%20got%20Aamir%20Khanzada%20in%20the%20car.%20They%20shot%20Aamir%20and%20disposed%20of%20his%20body.%20Then%20Sumit%20got%20himself%20shot%20in%20the%20leg%20-%20the%20plan%20was%20to%20make%20himself%20incapacitated%2C%20so%20he%20stays%20out%20of%20suspicion%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Sakore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20marred%20the%20script%20was%20an%20unexpected%20fight%20between%20the%20two%20killers.%20Sumit%2C%20unable%20to%20get%20medical%20help%20in%20time%2C%20died%20of%20excessive%20bleeding.%20Nakhade%20disposed%20of%20his%20body%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmir%20Khanzada's%20body%20was%20found%20near%20Karnala%20Bird%C2%A0Sanctuary.%20Sumit%20Jain's%20body%20was%20dumped%20by%20the%20roadside%20on%20Pen-Khopoli%C2%A0Road.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724949720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F851k5m2o_maharashtra-police-_625x300_05_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-property-dealer-gives-contract-to-kill-friend-then-a-plot-twist-6447295%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Contract%20Killing%20and%20then%20a%20miscalculation%20leading%20to%20a%20second%20death%20-%20these%20were%20what%20tied%20an%20abandoned%20car%20found%20near%20Mumbai%20and%20two%20missing%20property%20dealers%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20Police%20have%20found.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LIC%20receives%20demand%20notice%20of%20Rs%20605.58%20cr%20for%20short%20payment%20of%20GST%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724949600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-01%2F30%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1706613119-8233.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Flic-receives-demand-notice-of-rs-605-58-cr-for-short-payment-of-gst-124082901242_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20corporation%20has%20received%20a%20communication%2Fdemand%20order%20for%20interest%20and%20penalty%20for%20Maharashtra%2C%20LIC%20said%20in%20a%20regulatory%20filing%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Flic-receives-demand-notice-of-rs-605-58-cr-for-short-payment-of-gst-124082901242_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpU