n%20with%20racing%20began%20early%2C%20sparked%20by%20watching%20legends%20like%20Michael%20Schumacher%20and%20Lewis%20Hamilton.%20Despite%20growing%20up%20in%20a%20small%20town%20with%20limited%20resources%2C%20her%20dreams%20soared%20beyond%20the%20local%20landscape.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20on%2024%20July%201999%2C%20she%20was%20raised%20in%20a%20family%20that%20fought%20both%20financial%20hurdles%20and%20societal%20expectations%20to%20support%20her.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20were%20lectured%20on%20how%20to%20bring%20up%20girls%2C%20that%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20safe%20or%20proper%20for%20a%20girl%20to%20take%20such%20risks%2C%E2%80%9D%20Salva%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20my%20parents%20never%20imposed%20limits%20on%20me%20based%20on%20my%20gender.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC_K_8z-oW-F%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC_K_8z-oW-F%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC_K_8z-oW-F%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20(%40thebetterindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalva%E2%80%99s%20journey%20has%20been%20marked%20by%20challenges%2C%20particularly%20the%20high%20costs%20of%20F4%20training.%20As%20a%20business%20management%20graduate%2C%20she%20took%20on%20various%20jobs%20and%20ventures%20to%20fund%20her%20passion.%20Her%20relentless%20drive%2C%20coupled%20with%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20has%20been%20pivotal%20as%20she%20navigated%20the%20obstacles%20of%20pursuing%20her%20dreams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLiving%20your%20dream%20is%20a%20challenge%2C%20but%20I%20still%20believe%20in%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%2C%20acknowledging%20the%20emotional%20and%20physical%20toll%20her%20journey%20has%20taken.%20The%20emotional%20toll%20often%20left%20her%20feeling%20disconnected%20from%20loved%20ones%2C%20but%20the%20thrill%20of%20competition%20kept%20her%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalva%E2%80%99s%20racing%20career%20began%20in%202018%20with%20Formula%20LGB%20in%20India%2C%20and%20she%20quickly%20made%20a%20name%20for%20herself.%20Her%20most%20notable%20achievement%20came%20in%20the%202023%20F4%20UAE%20Championship%2C%20where%20she%20completed%20150%20laps%2C%20a%20number%20that%20speaks%20volumes%20of%20her%20resilience.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMotorsports%20are%20physically%20and%20mentally%20demanding%2C%20with%20challenges%20even%20greater%20for%20women.%20Salva%20shares%20that%20the%20intense%20conditions%20include%2040%C2%B0C%20temperatures%20inside%20the%20car%20and%2060-100%20kg%20braking%20pressure%20during%20curves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20body%20types%20and%20energy%20levels%20affect%20our%20endurance%20capacity.%20One%20loses%20around%204%20kg%20of%20body%20weight%20during%20the%20races.%20A%20racer%20needs%20the%20physique%20of%20a%20fighter%20pilot%2C%20including%20quick%20reflexes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20