ching%20child%20psychology%2C%20he%20found%20that%20establishing%20a%20solid%20foundation%20in%20the%20early%20years%20was%20the%20key%20to%20a%20well-rounded%20individual.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20he%20read%2C%20the%20more%20he%20understood%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20for%20parents%20to%20take%20a%20step%20back%2C%20observe%20their%20children%2C%20involve%20them%20in%20a%20daily%20routine%2C%20and%20let%20them%20develop%20into%20an%20individual%20on%20their%20own%2C%20without%20the%20need%20for%20praise%20or%20rewards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20exercise%20also%20helped%20him%20discover%20motivation%20within%20himself%20in%20his%20late%2030s.%20In%202022%2C%20he%20started%20sharing%20his%20learnings%20on%20parenting%20through%20his%20YouTube%20channel%20and%20Instagram%20under%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98TheCuriousParent%E2%80%99%2C%20with%20over%20a%20million%20following%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETake%205%20minutes%20a%20day%20to%20understand%20your%20child%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20he%20finished%20his%20schooling%20in%20Patiala%2C%20Harpreet%20pursued%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353376%2Fabhijeet-gan-rite-water-solutions-million-litres-clean-drinking-water-jal-jeevan-mission-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecivil%20engineering%20from%20IIT%20Bombay%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20working%20as%20a%20consultant%20for%20a%20few%20years%2C%20he%20started%20CoCubes%20with%20his%20roommate%20from%20college.%20Here%20they%20helped%20fresh%20graduates%20from%20Tier%202%20and%203%20cities%20find%20jobs%20in%20various%20corporations%2C%20which%20was%20often%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC7Owy-aI2tg%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%2