purity%20of%20iodised%20salt%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Sprinkle%20some%20salt%20on%20a%20potato%20slice%20and%20then%20squeeze%20a%20few%20drops%20of%20lemon%20juice%20over%20it.%20If%20the%20iodised%20salt%20is%20genuine%2C%20the%20potato%20will%20retain%20its%20natural%20colour.%20If%20the%20salt%20is%20mixed%20with%20common%20salt%2C%20the%20potato%20will%20turn%20blue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Smell%20Test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDissolve%20some%20sugar%20in%20a%20glass%20of%20water%20and%20give%20it%20a%20sniff.%20Pure%20sugar%20should%20have%20no%20smell.%20However%2C%20if%20the%20sugar%20has%20been%20tampered%20with%20urea%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20notice%20a%20pungent%20ammonia-like%20odour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20HCL%20Test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EJaggery%2C%20a%20natural%20sweetener%2C%20is%20another%20product%20that%20can%20be%20adulterated.%20To%20test%20for%20this%2C%20take%20some%20crushed%20jaggery%20and%20place%20it%20in%20a%20test%20tube.%20Add%20a%20few%20drops%20of%20Hydrochloric%20acid%20(HCL)%20to%20it.%20If%20the%20jaggery%20starts%20bubbling%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20sign%20that%20it%20has%20been%20mixed%20with%20impurities%20like%20baking%20soda%20or%20washing%20powder.%20Pure%20jaggery%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20will%20not%20react%20in%20this%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20rising%20cases%20of%20food%20adulteration%20and%20growing%20concerns%20over%20food%20safety%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20more%20important%20than%20ever%20to%20be%20vigilant.%20Taking%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352550%2Fhow-to-check-spices-purity-at-home-adulteration-indian-red-chili-powder-hing-turmeric%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejust%20a%20few%20minutes%20to%20perform%20these%20simple%20tests%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20help%20you%20ensure%20that%20the%20salt%2C%20sugar%2C%20and%20jaggery%20in%20your%20kitchen%20are%20pure%2C%20safeguarding%20your%20health%20and%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftoxicslink.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FPress%2520Release_English_Microplastics%2520In%2520Salt%2520and%2520Sugar_Toxics%2520Link%2520Study.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEating%20Lots%20Of%20%E2%80%98Sugar%20%26amp%3B%20Salt%E2%80%99%3F%20You%20Are%20Eating%20Lots%20of%20%E2%80%98Plastics%E2%80%99%20Too%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20Toxics%20Link%2C%20Published%20on%2013%20August%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724422529000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D362783%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amidst%20rising%20concerns%20over%20food%20adulteration%2C%20here%20are%20four%20DIY%20tests%20to%20detect%20impurities%20in%20salt%2C%20sugar%2C%20and%20jaggery%20at%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Khushi%20Arora%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F362783%2Fhow-to-test-adulterated-salt-sugar-jaggery-at-home-easy-simple-tests-steps-microplastics-watch-video-fssai%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%202%20Whistleblowers%20Used%20WhatsApp%20To%20Stop%20over%203000%20Child%20Marriages%20in%20Beed%20District%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mention%20of%20abuse%20and%20rape.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20a%20social%20worker%20at%20a%20government%20hospital%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Beed%20district%20was%20intrigued%20by%20a%20commotion%20that%20had%20ensued.%20Tatwashil%20Kamble%20(40)%2C%20who%20was%20at%20the%20hospital%20to%20donate%20blood%2C%20soon%20found%20the%20answer%20%E2%80%94%20the%20death%20of%20a%2017-year-old%20girl.%20While%20the%20cause%20of%20her%20death%20had%20been%20ascertained%20as%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emata%20mrutyu%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(death%20of%20a%20woman%20during%20childbirth)%2C%20Kamble%20knew%20there%20must%20be%20more%20to%20it.%20Sadly%2C%20talking%20to%20the%20people%20around%20him%20and%20the%20doctor%20left%20him%20aghast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20revealed%20that%20the%20girl%20had%20been%20to%20the%20hospital%20several%20times%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years%20over%20attempted%20pregnancies.%20The%20social%20worker%20was%20quick%20to%20deduce%20that%20this%20girl%20had%20been%20married%20at%20the%20age%20of%2014%20in%20a%20blatant%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330387%2Fias-officer-district-magistrate-saju-vaheed-balika-manch-prevent-child-marriage-south-tripura%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecase%20of%20child%20marriage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20shocking%20to%20him.%20But%20what%20the%20medic%20said%20next%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20just%20one%20of%20many%20such%20cases%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20compelled%20Kamble%20to%20dedicate%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20life%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20stopping%20child%20marriages%20in%20Beed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20this%2C%20he%20says%20that%20while%20a%20majority%20of%20such%20cases%20were%20bracketed%20as%20%E2%80%98maternal%20deaths%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20real%20cause%20of%20death%20is%20child%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamble%20was%20joined%20by%20Ashok%20Tangde%20(55)%20in%20his%20quest%20to%20put%20a%20halt%20to%20this%20widespread%20practice.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%20(CWC)%20%E2%80%94%20an%20autonomous%20institution%20formed%20under%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act%20(2015)%20%E2%80%94%20the%20duo%20has%20been%20working%20to%20ensure%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346951%2Fassam-pallabi-ghosh-impact-and-dialogue-foundation-child-human-trafficking-rehabilitation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafer%20world%20for%20girls%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Beed%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-1724157436.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tatwashil%20Kamble%20and%20Ashok%20Tangde%20have%20been%20working%20for%20the%20cause%20of%20stopping%20child%20marriages%20in%20India%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-1724157436.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-1724157436-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-1724157436-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-1724157436-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-1724157436-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362103%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETatwashil%20Kamble%20and%20Ashok%20Tangde%20have%20been%20working%20to%20stop%20child%20marriages%20in%20India%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Tatwashil%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20sugarcane%20is%20tied%20to%20the%20social%20evil%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98epicentre%20of%20sugarcane%20cutters%E2%80%99%2C%20Beed%20is%20deserted%20every%20year%20in%20October%20as%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20migrate%20to%20Western%20Maharashtra%20and%20Karnataka%20to%20cut%20cane%20for%20the%20factories%20in%20these%20regions.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CTo%20add%20to%20this%2C%20drought%20and%20poverty%20in%20t