%20of%20the%20child%20marriage%20survivors%20to%20understand%20what%20led%20them%20to%20the%20decision%20and%20to%20help%20them%20with%20resources%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Tatwashil%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20got%20there%20before%20Kamble%20could.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20family%20denied%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F247487%2Fkriti-bharti-saarthi-trust-jodhpur-rajasthan-child-marriage-rehabilitation-upliftment-child-brides-laxmi-sargara-women-inspiring-div200%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20child%20was%20being%20married%3C%2Fa%3E%20off.%20They%20insisted%20that%20a%20usual%20family%20function%20was%20being%20celebrated.%20When%20the%20police%20finally%20got%20them%20to%20admit%20the%20crime%2C%20the%20girl%E2%80%99s%20mother%20began%20threatening%20to%20end%20her%20life%20if%20the%20police%20did%20not%20allow%20the%20marriage%20to%20proceed.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamble%20was%20able%20to%20mitigate%20the%20dramatic%20turn%20of%20events%20by%20counselling%20the%20family%2C%20educating%20them%20about%20the%20distorted%20future%20that%20awaited%20the%20girl%2C%20and%20stopping%20the%20marriage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20impossible%20to%20expect%20a%20change%20overnight.%20A%20change%20in%20mindset%20will%20take%20time%2C%20he%20believes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChanging%20the%20narrative%20through%20digital%20intervention%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202011%2C%20Kamble%20shares%20that%20he%20and%20Tangde%20have%20been%20successful%20in%20stopping%20around%20250%20child%20marriages%20every%20year.%20Of%20these%20250%2C%20they%20say%20that%20over%2025%20children%20have%20been%20given%20a%20new%20lease%20on%20life%20through%20rehabilitation.%20He%20also%20claims%20that%20over%2070%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20survivors%20are%20rehabilitated%20each%20year%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E