eed%20good.%20The%20meat%20and%20spices%20were%20robust%2C%20not%20smelly%20or%20too%20oily%20as%20it%20is%20in%20many%20of%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20iconic%20%3Cem%3Ekheema%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplaces.%20The%20%3Cem%3Eporo%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Cem%3EParsi%3C%2Fem%3E-style%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20%3C%2Fem%3Eomelette)%20was%20pretty%20much%20the%20way%20my%20mom-in-law%20makes%20it%20and%20way%20tastier%20in%20this%20112-year-old%20place%20than%20omelettes%20(the%20far%20more%20expensive%20omelettes%20in%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20new%20cafes).%20Though%20the%20smiles%20all%20around%20were%20the%20best%20part%20of%20the%20breakfast.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Vig%20Refreshments%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Edal%20pakwan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F134874%2Fsindhi-cuisine-traditional-recipes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESindhi%3C%2Fem%3E%20speciality%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20combines%20lentil%20curry%20with%20crispy%20fried%20bread)%20is%20a%20draw%20at%20this%2075-year-old%20eatery.%20Praveen%20whose%20great-grandfather%20was%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20the%20%3Cem%3Epakwan%20%3C%2Fem%3Erecipe%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EFaroma%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20following%20the%20Partition%2C%20the%20family%20moved%20from%20Lahore%20to%20Chembur%20in%20Mumbai%20where%20they%20settled%20in%20a%20refugee%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FavbTdyvoEyY%3Fsi%3DtazIr0DNjTwUKMmV%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20what%20makes%20the%20%3Cem%3Edal%20pakwan%3C%2Fem%3E%20phenomenal%2C%20Praveen%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNormally%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20%3Cem%3Echanne%20ka%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chickpea%20gravy)%20with%20swee